{
  "texts": [
    "10 In other words, an aligned model pursues goals, has values or optimizes an objective function which correspond to the goals, values or objective function its designers want it to have.",
    "An AI model is misaligned if and only if it is not aligned.",
    "Misalignment can be understood in analogy with humans.",
    "Suppose I ask Magnus Carlsen to beat someone in chess.",
    "Suppose he loses intentionally."
  ]
}